#21205
Top of the Peak, Outside a HUGE Cave~
You've made it!!  Standing on the top of this mountain peak the view of the
kingdom is breathtaking.  To the north, east and south you can see all the
way to the edges of the magnificent Altat forest.  Far to the north-east you
can see a rather large clearing at the northern edge of the forest where
there appears to be a village.  Even farther to the north you can see the
magnificent river Cadera that flows directly into the forest.  To the north
of the village, on the river you can see a strikingly beautiful tower.  It
glows white, even from this distance, and appears as the most beautiful
building you have ever seen.  You must make a point of examining it from a
closer viewpoint.

After you take in the amazing view and catch your breath, reality finally
catches up with you.  You are standing outside an ENORMOUS cave-mouth.  Its
opening is easily more than fifteen meters around, and all of the rock around
it is scorched black.  You can hear some VERY heavy breathing coming from
inside and you think that it would be wise to get the hell out of here fast!
