This hall gets more amazing the farther you travel down it.  The sapphire is
as pure as that you would see in a jeweler's store.  The cuts and intricacies
of it are exquisite.  There are statues carved right out of the wall itself.
They depict cavaliers, monks, priests, wizards and dragon-kin.  The paintings
on the wall stand out as more beautiful that any you have seen.  Either the
Cavaliers who own this hall have wealth beyond imiganation or they have some
extremely talented friends.  The hall goes from the east to the west.
~
