Top of the Sapphire Staircase~
You are standing at the top of a magnificent sapphire staircase and facing
a hall that is created entirely out of sapphire.  It twinkles in the light
of magical fairie fires which seem to be imbedded in the walls themselves.
The statues and paintings lining the walls seem to glow with magical radiance
and the skill with which they have been crafted would cause even the simplest
collector to gasp.  The hall continues to the east and the stairs lead
down from here.
