#21293
Master Trainer's Antechamber~
The feeling of a magical influence comes over you in waves as you enter the
room. All around you are crystal statues of great warriors.  The paintings
along the walls depict several of the famous battles of the war with the
forces of Hel.  The largest statue in the room is a crystal version of the
Cavalier statue just below the sapphire trapdoor.  The statue here not only
shows the cavalier dressed in chainmail but it moves and shifts positions
to depict different attacking positions.  There is an arched entrance to the
east and a door to the south.
~
