Base of the Topaz Stairs~
This staircase looks quite remarkable.  Carved entirely out of topaz it shines
brighter than any other you've seen so far.  There are several illusions
dancing about the room, which constantly change form and appearance.  At one
point you see an elven mage throwing a lightning bolt at a demon, then the
next it depicts a Shin-Shun monk having his head caved in by a dragon-kin.
There is a large statue here of a Cavalier wearing no armor.  He appears
to be holding a spellbook in one hand but his shirt appears to have a coat
of arms upon it.  The stairs go up from here and there is a door to the south.
