Weapons Master's Antechamber~
The feeling of a magical influence comes over you in waves as you enter the
room. Crystal cabinets, housing various weapons, surround the room.  There
are swords, daggers, pole-arms, maces, flails, and many other weapons from
all around the realms.  All of the weapons appear to be of the very finest
quality and beneath each cabinet is a plaque with the name and origin of
the weapon.  There is also a crystal statue which is identical to the one
in the room beneath the sapphire trapdoor.  However, the statue here is
holding a vast assortment of weapons and moves and shifts positions and
weapons. There is an arched entryway to the east and a pearl door to the
north.
